{"tid":1812666,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【美心衛生嚇怕藍絲】【一人一twitter叫美國星巴克收番專營權】","createTime":"2020-01-05T16:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T16:08:23.000Z","uid":68779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"04acf92555ef1214407fde6233725e7e7d535f65","tid":1812666,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:00:33.000Z","msg":"[突發] 美心西餅發現有老鼠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1812521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1812521</a><br />\n<br />\n美心成個集團唔同牌子，無論中菜、西餐、元氣、星巴克，都因衛生問題上過各大報章。<br />\n我就係度諗，假如我排緊隊食元氣、simplylife, 但就無啦啦有人派傳單/ airdrop 以上既米奇開餐影片比我，我就算一向知餐飲業多衛生問題 (更何況好多藍絲以為好衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。但係你係我入去間鋪食野時先比啲咁既野我睇，我都冇胃口食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而且班藍絲一定會一傳十，十傳百。到時美心唔好又怪人搞到佢冇生意，要怪就怪美心連基本衛生都做唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外美心兩大利潤分別係星巴克同元氣，元氣股權大部分係新加坡基金，預左唔會收番專營權。但係星巴克係美國公司，或者有機會斷美心米路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左衛生，更重要係美心集團既主要人物有關言論。好多公司簽專營權合約時都會有形象相關條款。如果美國星巴克有心搞，我諗除左可以同美心解約，更加可以要佢幾億幾億咁賠番對星巴克形象做成既傷害，所以太子女一言唔止值千金，更值億元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果星巴克冇任何行動時，咁係咪代表美國星巴克公司都認同美心阿婆既言論呢？如果一唔覺意比班美國左膠人士知道時，星巴克係美國既生意睇怕好快拍得住香港，千其唔好睇少左膠力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nStarbucks 美國twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/starbucks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstarbucks&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1b9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=b30f6df2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/starbucks</a><br />\nCEO 既twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/howardschultz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhowardschultz&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1b9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=1029d9c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/howardschultz</a>"},{"pid":"31aebb7b5e5973e6e92e99f696609e5b1fa77f05","tid":1812666,"uid":263814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d21657392384ba73841b534fedd60f6dac4f89d","tid":1812666,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n叫佢藍加黃減最實制<br />\n藍加100%<br />\n黃免費<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0c28159216a09403ac06199061c376497fa1a6d7","tid":1812666,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}